data.description: This is the home you've been waiting for.  This gorgeous, almost new home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms.   This home is extremely spacious and features mid-level entry, with tons of natural light.  Enjoy an open kitchen floor plan, great for entertaining and open to the living and dining room.   The kitchen features a large island, double wall oven, and quartz counter-tops.  Head outside and enjoy evenings on your large spacious deck with an awning for those sunny days, and looks out to a beautiful tree line with water views.  Upstairs you'll find your primary suite and two additional bedrooms, hallway bath, as well as your laundry room equipped with a beautiful washer/dryer set.  On the lower level is your fourth bedroom, full bath, and an additional entertaining/recreation space.  This area provides ample shopping, restaurants, trails, and beaches nearby.  This is a great opportunity to own this almost new home.
